---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="Privacy Policy — AI Zest"
  description="AI Zest privacy policy — how we collect, use, and protect your personal data when you visit our website."
>
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-8 sm:py-12">
    <!-- Breadcrumb -->
    <nav class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-1.5 text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 mb-6" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
      <a href="/" class="hover:text-[#3B82F6]">Home</a>
      <span>/</span>
      <span class="text-gray-900 dark:text-white font-medium">Privacy Policy</span>
    </nav>

    <h1 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500 mb-10">Last updated: June 23, 2026</p>

    <!-- Section -->
    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">1. Introduction</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-2">
        AI Zest ("we," "our," or "us") respects your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you visit our website at <a href="https://aizest.net" class="text-[#3B82F6] hover:underline">aizest.net</a>.
      </p>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
        By using the Site, you agree to the collection and use of information in accordance with this policy.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">2. Information We Collect</h2>
      <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2">Personal Data</h3>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-3">
        While using our Site, we may ask you to provide us with certain personally identifiable information that can be used to contact or identify you. This includes:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed space-y-1 mb-4">
        <li>Email address (when subscribing to our newsletter via MailerLite)</li>
        <li>Name (optional, when contacting us)</li>
        <li>Any other information you choose to provide in communications</li>
      </ul>
      <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2">Usage Data</h3>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-3">
        We may also collect information about how you access and use the Site. This usage data may include:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed space-y-1">
        <li>Your IP address</li>
        <li>Browser type and version</li>
        <li>Pages you visit and time spent on those pages</li>
        <li>Referring URL</li>
        <li>Device information</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-3">
        We use the collected data for various purposes:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed space-y-1">
        <li>To operate and maintain our Site</li>
        <li>To send you newsletters and updates (only if you subscribed)</li>
        <li>To respond to your inquiries</li>
        <li>To understand how visitors use our Site and improve content</li>
        <li>To detect and prevent technical issues</li>
        <li>To comply with affiliate network requirements (e.g., Awin)</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">4. Cookies and Tracking</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-3">
        Our Site uses cookies and similar tracking technologies. For full details, please see our <a href="/cookie-policy" class="text-[#3B82F6] hover:underline">Cookie Policy</a>.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">5. Third-Party Services</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-3">
        We use the following third-party services that may collect information:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed space-y-1 mb-3">
        <li><strong>MailerLite</strong> — email newsletter delivery (data stored on MailerLite's servers)</li>
        <li><strong>Awin</strong> — affiliate marketing commission tracking</li>
        <li><strong>Cloudflare</strong> — CDN and security</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
        These third parties have their own privacy policies addressing how they use such information.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">6. Affiliate Disclosure</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
        Some links on our Site are affiliate links. If you click on an affiliate link and make a purchase, we may earn a commission at no extra cost to you. This helps us maintain and grow AI Zest. Our reviews remain unbiased — we only recommend tools we genuinely believe in.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">7. Your Data Protection Rights</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-3">
        Depending on your location, you may have the following rights regarding your personal data:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed space-y-1">
        <li><strong>Right to access</strong> — request copies of your personal data</li>
        <li><strong>Right to rectification</strong> — request correction of inaccurate data</li>
        <li><strong>Right to erasure</strong> — request deletion of your data</li>
        <li><strong>Right to restrict processing</strong> — request limited use of your data</li>
        <li><strong>Right to data portability</strong> — request transfer of your data</li>
        <li><strong>Right to withdraw consent</strong> — unsubscribe from emails at any time</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">8. Data Retention</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
        We retain your personal data only as long as necessary for the purposes set out in this policy. Newsletter subscribers' data is retained until you unsubscribe. Site usage data is retained for analytics purposes and then securely deleted.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">9. Security</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
        We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect your data. However, no method of transmission over the Internet is 100% secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">10. Children's Privacy</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
        Our Site is not directed to anyone under the age of 16. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children. If you believe a child has provided us with personal data, please contact us.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">11. Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
        We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes are effective immediately upon posting. We encourage you to review this page periodically.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">12. Contact Us</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
        If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:
      </p>
      <p class="text-sm text-[#3B82F6] mt-2">
        <a href="mailto:admin@aizest.net" class="hover:underline">admin@aizest.net</a>
      </p>
    </section>

    <!-- Disclaimer -->
    <div class="text-xs text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500 leading-relaxed text-center mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800">
      <p>Some links on this website are affiliate links. If you click through and make a purchase, we may earn a small commission at no extra cost to you.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
